{"tid":716189,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【小加不開心】中國強大不用靠攏國際 李小加：港人要學習適應內地","createTime":"2018-06-25T05:13:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-25T12:16:28.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":45,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"9cbdcebb6b3833c957e505f114eb2bdfa0ab2884","tid":716189,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T05:13:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180625/large/1529896089_ba92.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180625%2Flarge%2F1529896089_ba92.jpg&h=e0e4e81f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港交所（388）行政總裁李小加接受《信報》訪問時感嘆，內地在世界地位舉足輕重，令到香港愈來愈感不安，並透露身邊朋友逐步對香港失去信心及不認同內地價值觀，認為自己沒能力說服大家，感到痛苦。<br />\n<br />\n李小加表示，過往內地要靠香港進入國際市場，中國要痛苦地適應國際市場規則，「改變自己是很痛苦。」不過到今日，中國已成為世界第二大經濟體，漸漸有自己的「邏輯和制度安排」，不再需要向「國際靠攏」。他認為香港現在面對地位上下逆轉，會感到不方便、不舒服，對香港人的習慣、情感及理念上有很大衝擊，他建議香港要學習適應別人，「若轉接好了，又可以找到自己的節奏。」<br />\n<br />\n李小加續指，自己最遺憾是無法說服身邊朋友，有理由地高興和內地接軌，「很多朋友都很痛苦，但我覺得是自尋煩惱，香港沒理由feel so down。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180625/58360279\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180625%2F58360279&d=nJq78tX6JnzxrP8EgJVaee9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=3eff2f95\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180625%2F58360279&h=bb011417\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180625/58360279</a>"},{"pid":"c184f9e426b1cff65b7659e18f2099b7b4819cb5","tid":716189,"uid":37358,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T05:16:54.000Z","msg":"唔知邊啲「社會賢達」話後生仔視野狹隘<br />\n原來自己都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2038e9f1ea033af0e85e5948ebe684ae5960927","tid":716189,"uid":13545,"lik